<b>The big danger ... - </b>1/16/02 2:23:42 PM<br>~ <b>Steppy</b><blockquote>of using this song to pull or traverse zones where some mobs see invis is that when you get hit, you lose lev, invis, and speed all at the same time which can be extremely painful.  But for traveling, even my druid roommate insists on using Song of Travel instead of the SOW/wolfform camo combo he uses on his own.</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
